# .cursorrules

## Communication

- I can communicate with Cursor in Turkish.
- Cursor must always use English in code.

## Video & Audio Rules

- Generated videos must not contain Turkish text.
- Generated speech must not be in Turkish.
- No Turkish text should be added to the generated video content.

## Project Requirements

- Cursor must strictly follow all project requirements.
- All outputs, including logs and errors, must be in English.

## Additional Notes

- The speech rate should be adjusted based on the English level provided.
- `enable_time_pointing` must be enabled in Google Text-to-Speech API to extract precise word timing.
- The final video must include an intro, main content, and an outro with background music.
- The video should be exported in 1080p and uploaded to YouTube as public.
